summary: Relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 22W, page 75 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 911 North Northlake Way, Waterway 23 from Industrial Commercial with a 65 foot height limit/Conservancy Waterway (IC65/CW) to Commercial 2 with a 30 foot height limit/Conservancy Waterway (C230/CW). (Petition of Lake Washington Rowing Club, C.F. 301449, Appl. 9604179)
